cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CR, cs.SY 

This paper discusses the risks and challenges associated with learned optimization in advanced machine learning systems. It is likely to be classified under cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with the behavior of learned models such as neural networks. It also touches upon topics related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), and cybersecurity (cs.CR) as these fields are closely related to advanced machine learning systems. Additionally, the paper discusses the alignment of objectives in learned models, which is a topic of interest in control systems (cs.SY).
